  "additionalProperties": false,
  "description": "Static query-action affordance inventory for public action surfaces. Exposes target, cardinality, safety, destinations, formats, selection and confirmation commands, guards, and next actions.\n\nGenerated from `polylogue.surfaces.action_affordances.ActionAffordanceListPayload` by `devtools render cli-output-schemas`. Do not edit by hand.",
  "properties": {
